nd of cheese or shaming women for their dating preferences. This book focuses on Russian grass roots foreign policy after the annexation of Crimea, zeroing in on fetishization of Putin, militarization, sanctions, Russian-Turkish and Russian-American relations, FIFA World Cup and the COVID-19 pandemic.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2024) 4aPolitical Studies 2022. 4amanchesterhive variable pricing textbooks. 70(DE-588)4001307-80(DE-627)1063975910(DE-576)20884225XaAlltag2gnd 70(DE-588)4003846-40(DE-627)10438896X0(DE-576)208852972aAußenpolitik2gnd 70(DE-588)4006287-90(DE-627)1063780660(DE-576)208864962aBevölkerung2gnd 70(DE-588)4027058-00(DE-627)1062862340(DE-576)208968997aInnenpolitik2gnd 70(DE-588)4043152-60(DE-627)1048262740(DE-576)209054492aÖffentliche Meinung2gnd 70(DE-588)4055903-80(DE-627)1061564540(DE-576)209115866aSozialverhalten2gnd 70(DE-588)4072885-70(DE-627)1060939320(DE-576)209188553aInternationale Politik2gnd 70(DE-588)4112646-40(DE-627)1058356840(DE-576)209469684aAuswirkung2gnd 70(DE-588)4136010-20(DE-627)1056607870(DE-576)209665564aAnnexion2gnd 70(DE-588)4139132-90(DE-627)1056376290(DE-576)209691840aNationales Interesse2gnd 70(DE-588)4175043-30(DE-627)10536746X0(DE-576)209960949aPolitischer Prozess2gnd 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / World / Russian & Former Soviet Union.2bisacsh  aCOVID-19.  aFIFA World Cup.  aRussian-American relations.  aVladimir Putin.  ablackness in Russia.  aconjugal policing.  aforeign policy.  amemory of Second World War.  amemory of World War II.  apost-Soviet Russia.  asanctions.1 aGaufman, Elizaveta, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertManchester University Press 2023 eBook-Packagez9783111206455oZDB-23-MUP40uhttps://doi.or